from contracting the fields, a factor of 
from converting the integrals in  to sums, and
a factor of  from converting  Kronecker delta-functions
to the continuous delta functions in the first line of .
For operators of the second type one gets a factor
of  from contracting the  fields and a factor
of  from converting  Kronecker delta-functions.

